==English==

===Etymology===
Blend of [[sapient]] and [[heterosexual]] or [[homosexual]].

===Noun===
'''sapiosexual'''

# Someone of any [[sexual orientation]] who is sexually [[attracted]] by [[intelligence]].


===Adjective===
'''sapiosexual'''

# Of or pertaining to [[attraction]] or [[arousing]] sexually by [[intelligence]] and its use.


